NAME
    RT::Extension::SummaryByUser - portlets to show ticket counters per user

DESCRIPTION
    This extension ships with OwnerSummary portlet you can use in a
    dashboard and/or RT at glance. To make it available you must register it
    in the RT config using $HomepageComponents option. For more correct
    results and work without errors in any version prior to RT 3.8.5 you
    must apply patch that is shipped with this distribution in the patches
    directory. Also, DBIx::SearchBuilder has been updated as well, and you
    need 1.55_01 or newer.

    Don't forget to register plugin in the @Plugins config option.

REPOSITORY
        http://github.com/ruz/RT-Extension-SummaryByUser

